<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM6.7">
<l>paiyara viṉṉaṇaip paḷḷiyiṉāy paṇṭaiyō mallōmnām nīyukakkum</l>
<l>maiyari yoṇkaṇṇi ṉārumallōm vaikiyeṉ cēri varavoḻinī</l>
<l>ceyya vuṭaiyun tirumukamuñ ceṅkaṉi vāyuṅ kuḻaluṅkaṇṭu</l>
<l>poyyoru nāḷpaṭṭa tēyamaiyum puḷḷuvam pēcātē pōkunampī.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Sleeper on the bed that is the serpent with hoods!</l>
<l rend="indent">We are not [our] old selves. Neither are we women -</l>
<l rend="indent">with shining eyes [that have red] lines[and that are painted] with kohl</l>
<l rend="indent">- whom You desire.</l>
<l>You stop [Your] comings to our village after dawn.</l>
<l rend="indent">Enduring [Your] falsehood for one day,</l>
<l rend="indent">seeing the red clothes, the brilliant face, the red ripe fruit[-like] lips and curling hair,</l>
<l rend="indent">is enough.</l>
<l>Do not speak falsehood. Go, Lord!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
